==Exit list==
Until [[2002]], the mileposts on the Northeast Extension portion of I-476 started over at zero from the beginning of the Extension at the mainline Turnpike; additionally the exits were numbered sequentially as a continuation of the mainline Turnpike's numbering, starting with 31 at the [[Lansdale, Pennsylvania|Lansdale]] exit. In 2002, as part of a statewide transition from sequential to mileage-based [[Exit number|exit numbering]], [[PennDOT]] and the [[Pennsylvania Turnpike Commission]] renumbered the mileposts and exits along the entire length of I-476 as one continuous highway.

